{"type":"message","id":"196846bd","parentId":"389da42c","timestamp":"2026-04-20T11:26:27.730Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've completed the restoration of the OpenClaw workspace from GitHub. Let me now summarize what was restored and provide next steps to the user in Chinese since they asked in Chinese.\n\nSummary of what was restored:\n1. Core config files: AGENTS.md, BOOTSTRAP.md, HEARTBEAT.md, IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, TOOLS.md, USER.md, MEMORY.md\n2. Memory directory with daily notes (2026-03-15.md, 2026-03-25.md)\n\n\n3. Skills including desktop-control-win and skill-finder-cn\n4. The todo-api project folder\n5. Six business direction documents covering various OpenClaw monetization strategies\n6. Hidden configuration directories like .clawhub and .openclaw\n\nI should also mention setting up a .gitignore file to prevent sensitive files from being committed, verify that the remote origin is properly configured for future pushes, and confirm everything is ready to go.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 还原完成！\n\n从 GitHub 仓库 `kensoulstar/openclaw-workspace` 成功恢复了以下内容：\n\n**核心配置文件：**\n- AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, BOOTSTRAP.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md, HEARTBEAT.md, MEMORY.md\n\n**记忆文件：**\n- memory/2026-03-15.md\n- memory/2026-03-25.md\n\n**技能（skills）：**\n- desktop-control-win\n- skill-finder-cn\n\n**项目：**\n- todo-api/ 目录\n\n**业务方向文档：**\n- OpenClaw_赚钱方向_01~06 （共6份，涵盖文案、游戏外包、工程设计、客服、短剧改编、Agent编排等）\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 注意事项：**\n1. 原仓库没有 `.gitignore` 文件——建议创建一份排除 `state/`、`.clawhub/auth.json`、`.openclaw/` 中的敏感配置\n2. Git remote 已设置为 `https://github.com/kensoulstar/openclaw-workspace.git`（注意：当前网络环境下直接 push/pull 可能需要处理镜像问题）\n3. 本地 `.git` 目录保留，所有新文件需要手动 add & commit\n\n需要我帮你创建 .gitignore 或配置 SSH key 来方便后续同步吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":25205,"output":729,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0