{"type":"message","id":"b66d7269","parentId":"879c6d57","timestamp":"2026-04-20T11:58:27.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问当前安装的技能和插件。我需要查看本地文件系统来了解：\n1. skills/ 目录中的技能\n2. .openclaw/config.json 或类似配置文件中的插件设置\n\n让我先看看 skills 目录，然后检查 OpenClaw 配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"233963481","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ && echo \"=== SKILL.MD CONTENTS ===\" && for d in /home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace/skills/*/; do echo \"--- $(basename $d) ---\"; cat \"$d/SKILL.md\" 2>/dev/null | head -30 || echo \"(no SKILL.md)\"; echo \"\"; done","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":24429,"output":240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24669,"cost":{"input":0.048858,"output":0.00288,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.051738}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776686293079,"responseId":"chatcmpl-17xnkneiaeoi1exrk8vsljd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"11fcaf6c","parentId":"b66d7269","timestamp":"2026-04-20T11:58:27.687Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"233963481","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"总计 16\ndrwxrwxr-x 4 kensoulstar kensoulstar 4096  4月 20 19:25 .\ndrwxrwxr-x 9 kensoulstar kensoulstar 4096  4月 20 19:25 ..\ndrwxrwxr-x 4 kensoulstar kensoulstar 4096  4月 20 19:25 desktop-control-win\ndrwxrwxr-x 4 kensoulstar kensoulstar 4096  4月 20 19:25 skill-finder-cn\n=== SKILL.MD CONTENTS ===\n--- desktop-control-win ---\n---\nname: desktop-control\ndescription: Control desktop applications on Windows — launch, close, focus, resize, move windows, simulate keyboard/mouse input, manage processes, control VSCode, read clipboard, and capture screen info. Use when the user wants to interact with any running program, switch windows, type text, press shortcuts, open files in VSCode, manage running processes, or get system display information.\n---\n\n# Desktop Control — Full Windows Application Control\n\n## Publish-only note (ClawHub)\nThis Publish package includes scripts as `.ps1.txt` because Publish only accepts text files.\nAfter download, rename each `*.ps1.txt` to `*.ps1` and place them in a `scripts/` folder to use the skill.\n\nControl any desktop application on this Windows machine. Launch programs, manage windows, simulate input, control VSCode, and monitor processes — all via PowerShell scripts.\n\n## CRITICAL: Script Location\n\nAll scripts are located relative to this skill folder:\n\n```\nSKILL_DIR = ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/desktop-control/scripts\n```\n\nWhen running scripts, always use the full path:\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/skills/desktop-control/scripts/<script>.ps1\" -Action <action> [params]\n```\n\n## IMPORTANT: Safety Rules\n\n1. **Before closing windows** — Ask user for confirmation if the window might have unsaved work\n2. **Before killing processes** — Always confirm with user unless they explicitly asked to kill it\n\n--- skill-finder-cn ---\n---\nname: skill-finder-cn\ndescription: \"Skill 查找器 | Skill Finder. 帮助发现和安装 ClawHub Skills | Discover and install ClawHub Skills. 回答'有什么技能可以X'、'找一个技能' | Answers 'what skill can X', 'find a skill'. 触发词：找 skill、find skill、搜索 skill.\"\nauthor: 赚钱小能手\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: 🔍\n    requires:\n      bins: [clawhub]\n---\n\n# Skill 查找器 v1.0.1\n\n帮助用户发现和安装 ClawHub 上的 Skills。\n\n## 功能\n\n当用户问：\n- \"有什么 skill 可以帮我...？\"\n- \"找一个能做 X 的 skill\"\n- \"有没有 skill 可以...\"\n- \"我需要一个能...的 skill\"\n\n这个 Skill 会帮助搜索 ClawHub 并推荐相关的 Skills。\n\n## 使用方法\n\n### 1. 搜索 Skills\n\n```bash"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":38,"aggregated":"总计 16\ndrwxrwxr-x 4 kensoulstar kensoulstar 4096  4月 20 19:25 .\ndrwxrwxr-x 9 kensoulstar kensoulstar 4096  4月 20 19:25 ..\ndrwxrwxr-x 4 kensoulstar kensoulstar 4096  4月 20 19:25 desktop-control-win\ndrwxrwxr-x 4 kensoulstar kensoulstar 4096  4月 20 19:25 skill-finder-cn\n=== SKILL.MD CONTENTS ===\n--- desktop-control-win ---\n---\nname: desktop-control\ndescription: Control desktop applications on Windows — launch, close, focus, resize, move windows, simulate keyboard/mouse input, manage processes, control VSCode, read clipboard, and capture screen info. Use when the user wants to interact with any running program, switch windows, type text, press shortcuts, open files in VSCode, manage running processes, or get system display information.\n---\n\n# Desktop Control — Full Windows Application Control\n\n## Publish-only note (ClawHub)\nThis Publish package includes scripts as `.ps1.txt` because Publish only accepts text files.\nAfter download, rename each `*.ps1.txt` to `*.ps1` and place them in a `scripts/` folder to use the skill.\n\nControl any desktop application on this Windows machine. Launch programs, manage windows, simulate input, control VSCode, and monitor processes — all via PowerShell scripts.\n\n## CRITICAL: Script Location\n\nAll scripts are lo