{"type":"message","id":"17382554","parentId":"6f565275","timestamp":"2026-04-20T11:59:01.964Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the complete picture. Let me summarize:\n\n**Skills installed in workspace/skills/:**\n1. `desktop-control-win` - Windows desktop control (launch/close/focus windows, simulate input, etc.)\n2. `skill-finder-cn` - ClawHub skill finder/discovery tool (requires clawhub CLI)\n\n**Plugins configured:**\n- `lmstudio` plugin enabled - connects to local LM Studio server at http://192.168.31.71:1234/v1\n\n**Models available via LM Studio:**\n\n\nI'm seeing a comprehensive list of models ranging from the main qwen3.6 variants with different quantization levels, through the qwen3.5 options optimized for various use cases, and ending with embedding capabilities.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前安装情况\n\n### 📦 技能（Skills）— 2 个\n\n| 技能 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **desktop-control-win** | Windows 桌面控制 — 启动/关闭/聚焦窗口、模拟键盘鼠标输入、管理进程、VSCode 控制、剪贴板读写、屏幕信息捕获 |\n| **skill-finder-cn** | ClawHub 技能查找器 — 帮助用户发现和安装 ClawHub Skills（需要 `clawhub` CLI） |\n\n---\n\n### 🔌 插件（Plugins）— 1 个\n\n**lmstudio** ✅ 已启用\n- 本地 LLM 服务器：`http://192.168.31.71:1234/v1`\n- 认证方式：apiKey = \"lmstudio\"\n\n---\n\n### 🧠 可用模型（共 9 个）\n\n| 模型 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **主模型** `qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m` | 日常对话、推理 |\n| `qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q8_0` | 更高精度推理（更大） |\n| `qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled` | 原始完整版 |\n| `qwen3.5-27b-glm5.1-distill-v1` | 轻量级对话 |\n| `qwen3.5-9b-glm5.1-distill-v1@bf16` | 快速响应 |\n| `qwen3.5-9b-glm5.1-distill-v1@q4_k_s` | 低内存对话 |\n| `gemma-4-31b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled` | Gemma 推理 |\n| `gemma-4-31b-jang_4m-crack` | Gemma 变体 |\n| `text-embedding-nomic-embed-text-v1.5` | 向量嵌入（搜索/记忆） |\n\n---\n\n### 📋 其他发现\n\n**业务方向文档（6 份）：**\n- OpenClaw_赚钱方向_01 — 文案知识产权工业化矩阵\n- OpenClaw_赚钱方向_02 — 一人成军游戏制作与软件外包\n- OpenClaw_赚钱方向_03 — 硬核工程图纸与电子电路设计\n- OpenClaw_赚钱方向_04 — 客服外包与海量并发服务响应\n- OpenClaw_赚钱方向_05 — 短剧真人短剧工业化改编\n- OpenClaw_赚钱方向_06 — 科层制管理与Agent编排\n\n**todo-api** — API 项目（已在 todo-api/ 目录中）\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你安装更多技能或配置其他插件吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":28296,"output":1014,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29310,"cost":{"input":0.056591999999999996,"output":0.012168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.06876}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776686317671,"responseId":"chatcmpl-xgptz49zbfqdofufv9bvw"}}
