{"type":"message","id":"cacfdf5c","parentId":"a3c0fc27","timestamp":"2026-04-20T12:31:48.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to list the current skills. I just did this in my previous response, but let me provide a comprehensive answer again, including both workspace skills and built-in OpenClaw skills that are available as per my system prompt.\n\nFrom my previous analysis:\n- Workspace skills (in /home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace/skills/): desktop-control-win, skill-finder-cn\n- Built-in OpenClaw skills (from the system prompt's <available_skills>): coding-agent, healthcheck, node-connect, skill-creator, taskflow, taskflow-inbox-triage, tmux, video-frames, weather\n\n\nI should present this clearly in Chinese since that's what they've been using.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前技能清单\n\n### 📁 Workspace 自定义技能（2 个）\n\n| 技能 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| **desktop-control-win** | Windows 桌面控制 — 启动/关闭/聚焦窗口、模拟键盘鼠标输入、管理进程、VSCode 控制、剪贴板读写、屏幕信息捕获 |\n| **skill-finder-cn** | ClawHub 技能查找器 — 搜索和安装 ClawHub Skills（需要 `clawhub` CLI） |\n\n---\n\n### ⚙️ OpenClaw 内置技能（9 个）\n\n这些是 OpenClaw 自带的核心技能，已随系统安装：\n\n| 技能 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| **coding-agent** | 通过后台进程委托编码任务给 Codex、Claude Code 或 Pi 代理 |\n| **healthcheck** | 主机安全加固和风险配置检查（防火墙/SSH/更新状态） |\n| **node-connect** | 诊断 OpenClaw 节点连接和配对故障（Android/iOS/macOS） |\n| **skill-creator** | 创建、编辑、改进或审计 AgentSkills |\n| **taskflow** | TaskFlow 工作流引擎 — 用于编排复杂多步骤任务 |\n| **taskflow-inbox-triage** | TaskFlow 作者模式示例，用于收件箱分类处理 |\n| **tmux** | 远程控制 tmux 会话，适用于需要 TTY 的交互式 CLI |\n| **video-frames** | 使用 ffmpeg 从视频中提取帧或短视频片段 |\n| **weather** | 通过 wttr.in 或 Open-Meteo 获取天气和预报（无需 API Key） |\n\n---\n\n### 📊 统计\n\n- **自定义技能：** 2 个\n- **内置技能：** 9 个\n- **总计可用：** 11 个\n\n需要查看某个技能的详细说明，或者安装 ClawHub 上的其他技能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":28941,"