{"type":"message","id":"d9ff3600","parentId":"e6a0189c","timestamp":"2026-04-20T14:17:48.224Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so the skills are installed but with messy names like \"douyin-downloader-nodejszip\" instead of clean names. Let me fix these naming issues and also handle the plugins that don't have SKILL.md files properly.\n\nThe main issues:\n1. Names have \"zip\" appended (e.g., `douyin-downloader-nodejszip`)\n2. Some skills like `lossless-claw-enhanced-main` are plugins, not skills\n3. The OpenCode zip has config files, not a skill\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"136406388","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Fix the messy names and clean up\ncd /home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace/skills && \\\n\necho \"=== Renaming skills with 'zip' suffix ===\" \nfor d in *; do\n  if [[ \"$d\" == *\"zip\" ]] && [ -f \"$d/SKILL.md\" ]; then\n    # Remove trailing 'zip' from directory name\n    new_name=$(echo \"$d\" | sed 's/zip$//')\n    echo \"Renaming: $d -> $new_name\"\n    if [ ! -d \"$new_name\" ]; then\n      mv \"$d\" \"$new_name\" && echo \"  ✓ renamed\"\n    else\n      rm -rf \"$d\" && echo \"  (skipped, exists)\"\n    fi\n  fi\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Handling plugin directories without SKILL.md ===\" \nfor d in *; do\n  if [ ! -f \"$d/SKILL.md\" ] && [ -n \"$(ls $d/)\" ]; then\n    echo \"? $d: not a skill, contains:\"\n    ls \"$d/\" | head -3\n    \n    # For lossless-claw-enhanced-main - it's an OpenClaw plugin (not a skill)\n    if [[ \"$d\" == \"lossless-claw-enhanced-main\" ]]; then\n      echo \"  -> Moving to workspace root as plugin\"\n      mv \"$d\" /home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace/ 2>/dev/null && \\\n        echo \"✓ Plugin moved to workspace root\" || \\\n        echo \"? Failed to move plugin\"\n    fi\n  fi\ndone\n\n# Also check if there's an opencode directory that was extracted\nif [ -d \"OpenCode+╢α╓╟─▄╠σ╨¡═¼╣ñ╫≈┼Σ╓├\" ]; then\n  echo \"Removing OpenCode config dir (not a skill)\"\n  rm -rf \"OpenCode+╢α╓╟─▄╠σ╨¡═¼╣ñ╫≈┼Σ╓├\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Final clean skill list ===\" \ncount=0\nfor d in *; do\n  if [ -d \"$d\" ] && [ -f \"$d/SKILL.md\" ]; then\n    count=$((count + 1))\n    echo \"  $d\"\n  fi\ndone\necho \"\"\necho \"Total skills: $count\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":82605,"output":810,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83415,"cost":{"input":0.16521,"output":0.00972,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.17493}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776694646427,"responseId":"chatcmpl-sn1y8a90i2w0x7kbz7in"}}
