{"type":"message","id":"eab52fa5","parentId":"4b2f6769","timestamp":"2026-04-20T15:16:20.330Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"590982693","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776698180323}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c94c838","parentId":"eab52fa5","timestamp":"2026-04-20T15:16:30.104Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at both IDENTITY.md and USER.md, neither has been filled in - they're still blank templates. This is a fresh workspace that was just restored from GitHub backup.\n\nFrom what I can see:\n- The hostname is \"kensoulstar\" (from the filesystem path)\n- The username on the system is \"kensoulstar\" \n- There are memory files but none have been read yet for user context\n\nI should be honest - this is a fresh setup and we haven't had our \"first conversation\" where these things get defined. But I can offer to help establish this identity now.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n说实话——这是一个全新的工作空间。IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md 都还是空模板，我们还没有正式\"认识\"过。\n\n不过从系统里能看到：\n- **你的用户名**是 `kensoulstar`（主机名也是这个）\n- 你用的是 Linux 系统，运行着 OpenClaw Gateway\n\n---\n\n所以——你想现在聊聊吗？告诉我你的名字、你怎么称呼自己、你的时区……然后我可以帮你把这些写进文件。这样以后每次会话我都能记住。\n\n或者如果你更愿意先让我自己猜——我可以观察我们接下来的对话慢慢了解你 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":80812,"output":377,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81189,"cost":{"input":0.161624,"output":0.004524,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.166148}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776698180530,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b2fz3oylu7hsvl0lfwvi3h"}}
