{"type":"message","id":"7df6a13f","parentId":"f44a5bd1","timestamp":"2026-04-20T18:41:59.782Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我有了完整的信息。让我总结一下 lossless-claw-enhanced 插件的安装状态：\n\n1. **代码文件：** ✅ 已存在于 `~/.openclaw/workspace/lossless-claw-enhanced-plugin/`（版本 0.5.2）\n2. **OpenClaw Plugin 配置：** ✅ openclaw.plugin.json 存在且完整\n3. **插件启用状态：** ❌ **未在 openclaw.json 中注册**\n\n这意味着：\n\n\n- 源代码已经下载好了\n- 配置文件也准备好了\n- 但是 OpenClaw 网关还没有加载这个插件，所以需要在 openclaw.json 里手动添加配置才能启用它\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## lossless-claw-enhanced 插件安装状态检查\n\n### ✅ 部分已就绪\n\n**1. 源代码已存在：**\n- **位置：** `~/.openclaw/workspace/lossless-claw-enhanced-plugin/`\n- **版本：** v0.5.2（@martian-engineering/lossless-claw）\n- **描述：** DAG-based conversation summarization with incremental compaction\n\n**包含内容：**\n- openclaw.plugin.json — 插件配置 schema（完整，含 UI hints）\n- src/ — TypeScript 源代码\n- docs/、tui/ — 文档和终端界面\n- CHANGELOG.md、README_zh.md — 中文文档\n\n---\n\n### ❌ **未启用状态**\n\n查看 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`：\n```json\n\"plugins\": {\n  \"entries\": {\n    \"lmstudio\": {\n      \"enabled\": true\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**lossless-claw 插件未在 openclaw.json 中注册！**\n\n---\n\n### 📋 需要执行的操作\n\n**1. 启用插件：** 在 `openclaw.json` 中添加：\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"lmstudio\": { \"enabled\": true },\n      \"lossless-claw\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"contextThreshold\": 0.8,\n          \"incrementalMaxDepth\": -1,\n          \"freshTailCount\": 5\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**2. 重启 Gateway：** 使插件加载生效\n\n---\n\n### 🛠️ 功能说明\n\n这个插件提供 **DAG 式对话摘要**，当上下文窗口接近满时自动压缩历史消息：\n\n| 配置项 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|--------|--------|------|\n| `contextThreshold` | 0.8 | 触发压缩的阈值（0-1） |\n| `incrementalMaxDepth` | -1 | 增量压缩深度 (-1=无限) |\n| `freshTailCount` | 5 | 保护最近多少条消息不压缩 |\n| `dbPath` | ~/.openclaw/lcm.db | LCM SQLite 数据库路径 |\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 建议配置（适合星哥的场景）\n\n```json\n{\n  \"lossless-claw\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"contextThreshold\": 0.85,\n    \"incrementalMaxDepth\": -1,\n    \"freshTailCount\": 3,\n    \"summaryModel\": \"lmstudio/qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled\",\n    \"summaryProvider\": \"lmstudio\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n需要我帮你启用这个插件吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":90335,"output":926,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91261,"cost":{"input":0.18067,"output":0.011112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.191782}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776710491669,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3a6ln17y5aw1dy6s0zetlp"}}
