{"type":"message","id":"25dc7726","parentId":"7c385938","timestamp":"2026-04-20T19:18:01.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"星哥让我帮他启用 lossless-claw 插件。我需要修改 openclaw.json 配置文件来启用这个插件。\n\n首先我需要在配置中添加 lossless-claw 插件条目。根据之前的检查：\n- 插件源代码已经在 `~/.openclaw/workspace/lossless-claw-enhanced-plugin/` 中\n- openclaw.json 当前只启用了 lmstudio 插件\n- 需要添加 lossless-claw 的配置\n\n我需要：\n1. 读取当前的 openclaw.json\n2. 修改 plugins.entries 部分，添加 lossless-claw\n3. 使用 gateway config.patch API 来安全地更新配置\n\n\n4. 最后重启 gateway 使更改生效\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的星哥，我来帮你启用 lossless-claw 插件。先读取当前配置，然后修改：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"707508845","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.get","path":"plugins"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":90912,"output":361,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91273,"cost":{"input":0.18182399999999999,"output":0.004332,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.186156}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776712665511,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ojk5gmmyd8tyzjh4jovff"}}
