{"type":"message","id":"ea995ab8","parentId":"6cf29360","timestamp":"2026-04-20T19:32:56.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! The plugin is now properly installed and enabled. Let me summarize the final status for the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ lossless-claw 插件已安装并启用！\n\n### 📊 最终状态确认\n\n**1. 插件已在 OpenClaw Extensions 中激活：**\n- **路径：** `/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/extensions/lossless-claw/`\n- **版本：** v0.5.2\n- **状态：** ✅ enabled (已加载)\n\n**2. 配置文件更新 (`~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`)：**\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"lossless-claw\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"contextThreshold\": 0.85,\n          \"incrementalMaxDepth\": -1,\n          \"freshTailCount\": 3,\n          \"dbPath\": \"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/lcm.db\"\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"installs\": {\n      \"lossless-claw\": {\n        \"source\": \"path\",\n        \"sourcePath\": \"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/workspace/lossless-claw-enhanced-plugin\",\n        \"installPath\": \"/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/extensions/lossless-claw\",\n        \"version\": \"0.5.2\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**3. LCM 数据库已创建：**\n- **路径：** `/home/kensoulstar/.openclaw/lcm.db` (192KB)\n- **说明：** 用于存储上下文摘要和记忆压缩数据\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 当前配置含义\n\n| 参数 | 值 | 作用 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| `contextThreshold` | 0.85 | 当上下文使用率达到 85% 时触发压缩 |\n| `incrementalMaxDepth` | -1 | 增量压缩深度（-1 = 无限，自动计算） |\n| `freshTailCount` | 3 | 保护最近 3 条消息不被压缩 |\n| `dbPath` | ~/.openclaw/lcm.db | LCM 数据库存储位置 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔄 下一步：重启 Gateway\n\n需要重启 OpenClaw Gateway 才能使所有配置生效。你可以运行：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者我可以直接帮你执行？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":105376,"output":570,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105946,"cost":{"input":0.210752,"output":0.00684000000